---
title: Cheesy Shrimp Quesadilla Bar One recipe–endless ways to enjoy!
description: Everyone’s a winner when these customizable chicken quesadillas hit the table. Start with three fillings that are perfect for mixing and matching—fajita-spiced dark meat chicken, hearty black beans, and melty shredded cheese. Then, everyone can finish their quesadillas with sour cream, guacamole, and hot sauce on top, just the way they like it!
